<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">Collected on substrates of macrophytes and leaf packs, through all months of sampling (February 2018 through February 2019, dry and rainy season); also collected with a bucket light trap.</paragraph>
